    "text_1": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Welcome to TRENDYGOLF's exclusive guide to mastering your style game this First Major season! As the golf world gears up for one of the most prestigious tournaments of the year, it's time to elevate your wardrobe with top brands - including Nike, Puma, J.Lindeberg, Under Armour, and Original Penguin. Our experts have curated the perfect guide, showcasing each brand's top offerings, featuring everything from polos and trousers to caps and golf shoes, ensuring you're dressed to impress on and off the fairway.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["text_1"],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "NIKE: UNLEASH YOUR POTENTIAL",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Step onto the green with confidence in Nike's cutting-edge attire. As the brand favoured by pros worldwide, Nike's Augusta collection boasts an array of performance-driven pieces designed to elevate your game. Start with Nike's innovative golf shoes, engineered for optimal traction and stability on any terrain. Whether you prefer spiked or spikeless options, Nike has you covered.</p><p>Pair your footwear with Nike's signature golf trousers, crafted from lightweight, stretchy fabrics for unrestricted movement throughout your swing. Complete the look with Nike's stylish polo shirts, featuring moisture-wicking technology to keep you cool and dry under pressure. Top it off with a Nike cap - designed for comfort and breathability on the course. You'll feel ready to celebrate the First Major in style with Nike.</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_1": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "label": "SHOP NIKE SCRIPTING",
            "link": "https://trendygolf.com/pages/nike-scripting-the-first-major",
            "style": "dark-grey"
          }
        }
      },
