    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "PUMA: MAKE A STATEMENT",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Add a pop of personality to your First Major ensemble with Puma's bold and vibrant designs. Stand out from the crowd in their eye-catching polo shirts, featuring modern patterns and striking colour combinations. Crafted from highly breathable fabrics, Puma's polos offer style and performance on the fairway.</p><p>Pair your polo with Puma's sleek golf trousers - designed for maximum flexibility and comfort throughout your round. Complete the look with a Puma cap, showcasing the brand's iconic logo for a touch of athletic flair. Step into Puma's high-performance golf shoes, featuring responsive cushioning and durable traction for unmatched comfort and stability. With Puma, you'll make a statement on and off the course.</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_1": {
