          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "J.LINDEBERG: TIMELESS ELEGANCE",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For those who appreciate understated sophistication, J.Lindeberg delivers with their classic yet contemporary First Major collection. Elevate your style with J.Lindeberg's impeccably tailored polo shirts, crafted from luxurious fabrics for a refined look and feel. Add a layer of warmth with J.Lindeberg's stylish mid-layers, perfect for those early morning tee times.</p><p>Pair your top with J.Lindeberg's tailored golf trousers, designed for the modern golfer who values performance and aesthetics. Step into J.Lindeberg's premium golf shoes, featuring sleek silhouettes and superior craftsmanship for unparalleled comfort and support. With J.Lindeberg, you'll exude timeless charm and sophistication on the fairways.</p>"
