        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Dominate the greens in Under Armour's performance-driven attire. Start with their versatile hoodies, perfect for layering on cooler days or early morning rounds. Crafted from lightweight, breathable fabrics, Under Armour's hoodies offer superior comfort and warmth without sacrificing mobility.</p><p>Pair your hoodie with Under Armour's sleek polo shirts, featuring sweat-wicking technology to keep you dry and comfortable throughout your round. Complete the look with Under Armour's high-performance golf shoes, engineered for stability and traction on any terrain. With Under Armour, you'll feel unstoppable on the course, ready to tackle any challenge that comes your way.</p>"
