        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Add a touch of nostalgia to your Augusta ensemble with Original Penguin's retro-inspired designs. Channelling the spirit of classic golf style, Original Penguin's polo shirts feature timeless patterns and playful accents that pay homage to the sport's rich heritage. Layer up with Original Penguin's stylish mid-layers, perfect for transitioning between the course and clubhouse.</p><p>Pair your top with Original Penguin's tailored trousers, crafted from premium fabrics for a comfortable fit and classic look. With Original Penguin, you'll capture the essence of golf's golden era while making a statement that's all your own.</p>"
